contentheadline.headline: List of military corps by name

contentrichtext.text: This is a '''list of military [[corps]]''' arranged by name. * [[Afrika Korps]] * [[Australian Corps]] * [[Australian and New Zealand Army Corps]] * [[British Cavalry Corps]] * [[Canadian Corps]] * [[Cavalry Corps Schmettow (German Empire)]], a unit of the Imperial German Army during [[World War I]] * [[Desert Mounted Corps]] (formerly ''Desert Column'') * [[Ersatz Corps]], a unit of the Imperial German Army during World War I * [[Gebirgskorps Norwegen]] * [[Guards Corps (German Empire)]], a unit of the Imperial German Army prior to and during World War I * [[Guards Reserve Corps]], a unit of the Imperial German Army during World War I * [[Headquarters Allied Rapid Reaction Corps]] * [[Landwehr Corps]], a unit of the Imperial German Army during World War I * [[2nd Division (New Zealand)|New Zealand Corps]] {{seealso|List of military corps by number}} [[Category:Lists of military units and formations|Military corps by name]]
